What is managed by the client in a Platform as a Service (PaaS) environment?
A. Applications and data.
B. Runtime, middleware, OS.
C. Compute, storage, network.
D. None of the above. The entire stack is managed by the cloud service provider.
Answer: B
Which statement about Cloudant's support features is TRUE?
A. No multi-master replication.
B. No geo-load balancing.
C. No difficulty adding new regions.
D. Poor data throttling.
Answer: D
Reference:
https://cloudant.com/wp-content/uploads/IntrotoCloudantDeck.pdf
